aiAssistant.title: Lumsebenti Lwe-AI
aiAssistant.subtitle: Buza imibuzo yakho futsi utfole tincomo letilungiselelwe wena
aiAssistant.welcomeMessage: Sawubona! Ngingumsebenti wakho we-AI. Ngingakusita kanjani namhlanje?

mockResponses.response1: Ngiyakwati! Singakusita ngemahlanganweni etimali lamaningi. Bheka ikhasi lethu le-Finance ukutfola lwati lolugcwele ngemahlanganweni letako.
mockResponses.response2: Kuphepha kwakho kubalulekile. Singakusita ngetindawo tekuphepha letiphephile, tinombolo tesimo lesiphuthumayo, nelusekelo lwemtsetfo. Bheka ikhasi lethu le-GBV Support.
mockResponses.response3: Sinemabhokisi okupha emkhiqizweni yekuhlambuluka kuyo yonkhe iNingizimu Afrika. Bheka ikhasi lethu le-Sanitary Aid ukutfola indawo lesedvute nawe.
mockResponses.response4: Singakuxhumanisa nelusito lwemtsetfo lwamahhala. Legal Aid South Africa iniketa lusito lwamahhala kubomake labadinga. Shayela 0800 110 110.
mockResponses.response5: Uma usesimweni lesiphuthumayo, shayela 10111 (emaphoyisa) noma 0800 428 428 (GBV Command Centre) ngekushesha. Kuphepha kwakho kubalulekile.

footer.disclaimer: Lumsebenti lwe-AI luyasita kodvwa alukhetsi indawo yekuceceshwa kwetinsingati. Uma udinga lusito lwesimo lesiphuthumayo, xhumana netinsingati.

about.title: Nge-EmpowerHub
about.subtitle: EmpowerHub icinisa bomake eNingizimu Afrika ngekuniketa tincomo tetimali letilungiselelwe wena kanye nemibono, lusito loluleshesha lwe-GBV kanye netindawo tekuphephela letiphephile, kanye nekufinyelela emabhokisini ekupha awekucoceka. Lesi sisombululo lesihlanganisiwe sibonisa kutinikela kwetfu ekuciniseni kutimela, kuphepha, nesitfunti.
about.missionText: Kutfutfukisa lipulatifomu lelihlanganisiwe lelicinisa bomake eNingizimu Afrika yonkhe ngekuniketa tinsita tekusekela letiphelele letibhekene nekutimela ngetimali, kuphepha kwemuntfu, kanye netidingo tetinhloko tekucoceka esisombululweni lesinye lesifinyelelekayo.

about.techDescription: EmpowerHub isebentisa buchwepheshe besimanje kuniketa lipulatifomu lwelusito lelihlanganisiwe. Umboniso wetfu wanje ubonisa sikhombimsebentisi kanye nemsebenzi wetinhloko, kanye nemicabango yekuhlanganisa tincumo letitfutfukile letibandakanya:
about.demoNote: Lolu mboniso ubonisa umcabango wesisombululo lesihlanganisiwe, lesiklanywe kuvumela kutfutfukisa lokutimele kwetincumo kuyilapho kugcinwa lwati lwemuntfu losebentisako loluhambisanako. Kwakha lokuyitincenye kuvumela kutfutfukisa kwekusasa ngaphandle kwekuphatsamisana umsebenzi wetinhloko.
